      "comment": "MIDNIGHT FURY (4) missed the frame last time, finishing 4th (19.64) last time in a Grade 4 at Bulli. Has never been out of the money this course and distance including one win. Should be very hard to beat this time. SANDI KINGDOM (3) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at Bulli over 340m. Must be included in calculations. KARLI MULWEE (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Taree Super Track over 300m behind Ocean's Pearl (18.21) in a Grade 3/4. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to run well. MR. SPECKLE (8) has been freshened for this and can hit the frame.",
